name: SpaceX
short: Get various information about SpaceX using the SpaceX-API.
description: Get various information about SpaceX using the SpaceX-API. You can also use the Space cog from kennnyshiwa (https://github.com/kennnyshiwa/kennnyshiwa-cogs) for more about space in general, space pics, Astronomy Picture of the Day from Nasa, ISS location ...
end_user_data_statement: This cog does not persistently store data or metadata about users.
